+  intent inference (AM-F014), scope auto-narrowing with explicit constraint walking (AM-F015),
+  and capability-to-epic automation (AM-F016 + WI-F007), every specify-product run relies on
+  manual selection that misses constraints and produces shallow epics. Market brief gap 4
+  confirms: no AI coding tool connects the intent behind a feature to test generation in
+  a persistent artifact chain. The concrete failure: a constraint referencing an unknown
+  feature ID causes configure-capabilities to block with no clear recovery path.
+
