+      Quantification regex in validate-intent-epics catches any non-numeric constraint
+      value; no-TBD rule in validate-intent-epics catches placeholder tokens across
+      all string fields; the pipeline blocks on first violation.
+  - scenario: >
+      Given a cross-tree constraint that references a feature ID not found in any
+      domain-taxonomy file, when configure-capabilities walks that constraint, then
+      scope auto-narrowing fails with an orphan-reference error.
+    impact: >
+      specify-product Stage 3 blocks; the entire pipeline stalls until the KB inconsistency
