+    mitigation: >
+      validate-kb-extension pre-flight checks every feature ID in every constraint
+      before configure-capabilities runs; any dangling reference is a blocking failure
+      emitted before the constraint walk begins.
+  - scenario: >
+      Given a generated epic that is missing a mandatory field, when validate-intent-epics
