+      identify the missing field from the validator output. Solo-dev impact: every stall
+      is a solo context-switch with no team to help triage.
+    mitigation: >
+      Template completeness check in generate-intent-epics before write: every mandatory
+      field is verified non-null before the file is written; structured failure emitted
+      with field-level detail if derivation fails.
+  - scenario: >
+      Given a generated epic whose kb_source.capability points to a feature ID that has
+      been deprecated or renamed in the domain-taxonomy, when validate-intent-epics runs
+      the traceability check, then the epic fails with dangling_kb_source.
+    impact: >
+      Epic traceability breaks; the audit trail from epic to KB feature is severed.
