+  Augment Code SOC2 guide, Probo compliance guide). The compliance ratchet fires for this
+  product: profile compliance.categories includes 'ai-usage-traceability', mandating 100%
+  of play-produced commits carry an AI-authorship commit trailer. Current status is PARTIAL —
+  commit-level attribution is not yet enforced across all 42 plays. For a solo contributor,
+  every unattributed AI commit represents a 100% attribution gap for that commit with no
+  human-authored commits to triangulate from.
+
