+  Ensure 100% of play-produced commits carry an AI-authorship commit trailer and every
+  inferred decision is recorded in a decision manifest with tier-rationale, making the
+  AI-vs-human attribution chain auditable on demand for compliance officers reviewing
+  a solo-dev Garura-managed project.
