+  - "WI-F011 Test Synthesis at Advanced depth: test synthesis for ≥ 1 language ecosystem (Node/TypeScript) at launch; synthesized tests trace to scenarios in the intent epic; tests are executable out-of-box without configuration"
+  - "WI-F012 RCA Template at Advanced depth: every defect filed against a Garura play has RCA evidence before a fix is proposed; 5-whys structure in RCA template enforced by fix-it"
+  - "WI-F013 Fix-It Loop Closure at Advanced depth: fix-it closes ≥ 95% of filed defects without reopening; mandatory regression test after every fix; loop evidence preserved across sessions"
+  - "Eval coverage sweep: audit all 42+ plays for step eval attachment; fill gaps in eval coverage"
+  - "Scenario eval audit: verify every capability in scope has scenario evals for ≥ 2 success and ≥ 2 failure scenarios"
