+
+business_rules:
+  - "Mandatory for L3+ — every play must have step evals generated from intent.yaml before the play ships (WI-F010)"
+  - "Mandatory for L3+ with test automation — synthesized tests must trace to scenarios; no test without a traceable scenario (WI-F011)"
+  - "Mandatory for L3+ production systems — every defect resolution goes through structured RCA before a fix is proposed (WI-F012)"
+  - "Mandatory (never excludable) — fix-it loop closure is required for every defect; the fix-it play is the only approved path for defect resolution (WI-F013)"
+  - "Regression test is mandatory on every fix — no fix-first-test-later; regression test is required before fix-it marks the defect as closed (WI-F013)"
+  - "5-whys structure in RCA template — fix-it enforces RCA depth before proposing any fix; shallow RCA is a blocking failure"
+
