+  - "Secondary consumer: derive-nfr-spec — reads quality-profile.yaml and intent epics constraints together to produce the NFR specification; the security_profile.compliance_mandates section is the primary NFR input surface"
+  - "Risk register brownfield note: 57% of features are LIVE at the time of this quality profile; regression_risk entries are active threats against shipped code; delivery_risk entries are active threats against unshipped features (PARTIAL/PLANNED); build-arch should weight regression_risks higher in architectural decision gates"
